; domain.
;
; This registry has the information in human and machine readable form.
;
; The format follows: 
; (lines starting with a ; are comments. also see the Bind Operators
; Guide)
; (A RRs that end with ";inaddr" are not included in the inaddr zone.)
;
;<name> <ttl>   <class> <type>  <data>
; where: <name> - <letter> [ <letter-digit-hyphen>* <letter-digit>]
;               and is the domain (host or mailbox) name being described
;               If blank use the previous one.  NOTE: this file inherits
;               .home.drummond.us. as a (trailing) part of the <name>.
;       <ttl>   - the Time To Live for this records (all records for a name
;               should have the same TTL) in seconds.
;       <class> - (See Domain:PPLegals.Txt for legal Dclass.
